Subject: [PATCH] Add Gemini-based grammar exercise generation

- lib/gemini.ts: extracted shared callGemini() + targetItemCount() helpers
  from the vocabulary generator (no behavior change there)
- New generateGrammarSet(): produces a mix of SENTENCE_BUILDER,
  ERROR_SPOTTING, FILL_BLANK_GRAMMAR, VERB_CONJUGATION, and
  MULTIPLE_CHOICE_GRAMMAR items from a lesson's content, ~1 item per 60
  words (4-20 range). VERB_CONJUGATION items include a rule explanation
  and a full conjugation table as requested.
- app/api/lessons/[id]/generate/route.ts: dispatches to the right
  generator by anex instead of a single if-check; GRAMMAR now works,
  LISTENING_WRITING/SPEAKING still return 501 (need audio/TTS handling
  first, planned as a separate PR)

Depends on: feature/exercise-generation-vocabulary (Anex enum + ExerciseSet
model). Branch this PR on top of that one, or wait until it merges to main.
